entry.def: Eurasian means concerned with or relating to both Europe and Asia.
A Eurasian is a person who has one European and one Asian parent or whose family comes from both Europe and Asia.

means.word_mean: 1. a person of mixed European and Asian descent
1. relating to, or coming from, Europe and Asia;
